person.bio: Ahmed is an Automation Software Testing Engineer, started his carreer at Codescalers, and now has about a year experience in Cloudcomputing software. Engineer fell in love with Threefold I believe that Threefold is changing the world by building the new neutral internet, it's a great experience to be part of this.
